Swipe at your foe, knocking them back.
Knockback your foe with the butt of your rifle. Be careful not to break it.
<c=@abilitytype>Survival.</c> Entangle foes around you with vines. Entangled foes bleed and are immobilized until the vines are destroyed.
<c=@abilitytype>Physical.</c> Charge and knock down your foe.
Fire your arrow cart at the target area. Arrows that hit bleed the target.
Fire your arrow cart at the target area. Arrows that hit cripple the target.
<c=@abilitytype>Manipulation.</c> Give allies Illusion of Life at the target location, allowing them to get up from downed state and keep fighting. Fully revives allies if they kill a foe.
Signal Merri to fire the cannon at target location.
Blast your foe repeatedly with both pistols.
